# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository and on checkout.
# This repo is developed on Linux/WSL; a Windows-side editor had rewritten the
# working tree to CRLF, producing 151 phantom "modified" files with no content
# change. Declaring LF policy makes git treat those as clean and prevents recurrence.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Never touch binary artifacts.
*.bundle binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
